div2.p:
The proper noun designation for a place, natural feature, or political
		jurisdiction. Examples include: Appalachian Mountains; Baltimore, Md.;
		Chinatown, San Francisco; and Kew Gardens, England.

Number of additional rows in a vertical straddle. Value is a number;
		default value is "0" to indicate one row only, no vertical span. Available in
		entry only.
